replies.body:
@Meddler please, please talk about Lissandra. {{champion:127}} 

I don't know what happened but she feels SO bad since the start of season 8.
She wasn't strong before but now she is just bad. I love her but I can completely understand her low pick rate.

I feel like I'm dealing no dmg, I have no sustain and no range. And there are better champions for CC.
Even if I manage to find the perfect spot in team fights it's just not rewarding at all.

Please just pick Lissandra as one of the topics for Fridays post.
